tags.name: a11y-collapse
tags.description:
`a11y-collapse`

Events:

  * `a11y-collapse-detached` - Fires when detatched, so that parent radio group will no longer listen for it.

  * `toggle` - Fires when toggled.

  * `a11y-collapse-toggle` - Deprecated. Fires when toggled.

  * `expand` - Fires when expanded.

  * `collapse` - Fires when collapsed.

  * `a11y-collapse-click` - Fires when clicked.

Attributes:

  * `accordion` {`boolean`} - accordion-style: whole header acts as button? default is just icon.

  * `disabled` {`boolean`} - is disabled?

  * `expanded` {`boolean`} - icon when expanded

  * `icon` {`string`} - icon for the button

  * `icon-expanded` {`string`} - icon when expanded

  * `label` {`string`} - label for the button

  * `label-expanded` {`string`} - optional label for the button when expanded

  * `tooltip` {`string`} - tooltip for the button

  * `tooltip-expanded` {`string`} - optional tooltip for the button when expanded

Properties:

  * `accordion` {`boolean`} - accordion-style: whole header acts as button? default is just icon.

  * `disabled` {`boolean`} - is disabled?

  * `expanded` {`boolean`} - icon when expanded

  * `icon` {`string`} - icon for the button

  * `iconExpanded` {`string`} - icon when expanded

  * `label` {`string`} - label for the button

  * `labelExpanded` {`string`} - optional label for the button when expanded

  * `tooltip` {`string`} - tooltip for the button

  * `tooltipExpanded` {`string`} - optional tooltip for the button when expanded

tags.name: a11y-collapse-group
tags.description:
`a11y-collapse-group`

Events:

  * `a11y-collapse-detached` - Fires when detatched, so that parent radio group will no longer listen for it.

  * `toggle` - Fires when toggled.

  * `a11y-collapse-toggle` - Deprecated. Fires when toggled.

  * `expand` - Fires when expanded.

  * `collapse` - Fires when collapsed.

  * `a11y-collapse-click` - Fires when clicked.

Attributes:

  * `global-options` - an array of globalProperties to override every a11y-collapse item
For example, {"icon": "arrow-drop-down"} would set every item's icon to "arrow-drop-down"

  * `radio` {`boolean`} - is every a11y-collapse item radio button?

  * `__items` {`any[]`} - is radio button

  * `accordion` - accordion-style: whole header acts as button? default is just icon.

  * `disabled` - is disabled?

  * `expanded` - icon when expanded

  * `icon` - icon for the button

  * `icon-expanded` - icon when expanded

  * `label` - label for the button

  * `label-expanded` - optional label for the button when expanded

  * `tooltip` - tooltip for the button

  * `tooltip-expanded` - optional tooltip for the button when expanded

Properties:

  * `globalOptions` - an array of globalProperties to override every a11y-collapse item
For example, {"icon": "arrow-drop-down"} would set every item's icon to "arrow-drop-down"

  * `__items` {`any[]`} - is radio button

  * `disabled` - is disabled?

  * `label` - label for the button
